text: ao banda anak del mean chomnue. chaur puok anak romluk nouv nie k meat robsa a l laoh del trong ban bratan aoy puok anak nowpel del mnoussa muoy krom mean bamnng chng samleab puok anak daoy dai robsa puokke haey trong ban karpar puok anak aoy ruochphot pi kandabdai robsa puokke . haey chaur puok anak kaotakhlach a l laoh haey chaur aoy banda anak del mean chomnue brakl kar touk chetd tow champoh a l laoh
